<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>603</hymn_number>
<title>yé hé huá shì zhàn shì 迦南603</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yé hé huá shì zhàn shì shì wǒ sì wéi de dùn pái
 tā měi tiān shēn shǒu lái dā jiù wǒ shì zhěng jiù wǒ de gāo tái
 yé hé huá shì zhàn shì gāo shān jiàn tā yě dī tóu
 yé hé huá shì zhàn shì hóng hǎi jiàn tā yě ràng lù
 quán de chōng mǎn tā de róng yào yī qiè dōu gěi shén xiào lì
 zhè gè shí dài yào hū hǎn yé hé huá shì zhàn shì
 bù tóng zhǒng zú bù tóng miàn kǒng dōu yào lái gēn suí tā
 fán gēn suí tā de méi yǒu yī gè luò hòu yé hé huá shì zhàn shì.</lyrics>
</song>